&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/aws/polly-text-to-speech-in-47-voices-and-24-languages/&#34;&gt;Amazon Polly ‚Äì Text to Speech in 47 Voices and 24 Languages&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

